(Whenever I'm sad,)

00:12:51.380 --> 00:12:52.939
(I dance.)

00:12:52.940 --> 00:12:53.899
(As long as I'm dancing,)

00:12:53.900 --> 00:12:56.020
(all my worries just float away.)

00:12:57.340 --> 00:12:58.619
A newly crowned emperor dancing

00:12:58.620 --> 00:13:00.899
on the throne itself at his accession.

00:13:00.900 --> 00:13:02.659
This is unheard of.

00:13:02.660 --> 00:13:04.361
Utterly absurd.

